    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean, i really don't have the time to go to a clinic right now and it's pretty expensive here anyway. if it's just conjunctivitis, can't i just use some warm compresses and those refreshing eye drops for a few days to see if it clears up? i'm sure it's nothing serious.",
