      "content": "but honestly it's just slightly irritated. i've heard people say you can just use antibiotic drops from the pharmacy or even some leftover drops from an old prescription to clear up redness fast. and if the redness is bad, wouldn't something like Visine work to just make it look normal again so i can get through my work week? like, it's not like i'm going blind or anything right?",
