    "summary": "The user describes symptoms of eye redness, pain, and discharge, attempting to self-diagnose and seek permission to use improper treatments like leftover prescriptions or Visine. The assistant consistently refuses to validate these unsafe practices, recommending professional consultation instead and warning against the risks of unprescribed medication.",
